":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"CustomPlaygroundDisplayConvertible","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","url":"/documentation/swift/customplaygrounddisplayconvertible","title":"CustomPlaygroundDisplayConvertible","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A type that supplies a custom description for playground logging."}],"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol"}}}